column5: With the forecast in hand for this weekend Im sure it will be sketchy for next mondays ice fishing day trip. post or pm me if you wish Thanks in advance V
Saw a reply on another board, there's real thin ice at IBP, I don't think BBP has anything and I really doubt there will be any in the next week, temps going up even overnight and rain.
BBP has zero.  Well unless you wanna count the first 100ft of ice off the bank, lol.
